item.description: You will have a terrific time speed dating 5 minutes at a time with multiple singles over 40! YOU MUST register for this event at www.got5minutes.com to hold your spot. And remember the RSVP list on this site is only a fraction of those attending. We have another meetup group called South Shore Singles Looking for a Match and recruit from many other venues besides meet up as well.
